{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "public/**",
      "use": "@vercel/static"
    },
    {
      "src": "api/**/*.js",
      "use": "@vercel/node"
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/api/(.*)",
      "dest": "/api/$1"
    },
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "/public/$1"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

### **Step 3: Also Check Your `api/chat.js` File Location**

Make sure your file structure looks EXACTLY like this:
```
virevo-chatbot/
├── api/
│   └── chat.js          ← Your API file
├── knowledge/
│   └── (your .md files)
├── public/
│   └── index.html       ← Your frontend
├── vercel.json          ← THIS FILE IS CRITICAL
└── package.json
